(Optional guard ENFORCE_CONSENSUS_WRITE requires consensus_write_context.) Tj
T*
(- Tx index maintenance is in the same LMDB write transaction as block writes and deletes so tx) Tj
T*
(lookup stays consistent with chain state.) Tj
T*
(- Persistent witness pruning: compact_pruned_witnesses\(\) now rewrites eligible old block records) Tj
T*
(so witness maps and tx_list_full payloads are actually removed from disk as the tip advances.) Tj
T*
(- Reads: get_by_height/get_by_hash expand compact, prune witnesses in-memory if past retention) Tj
T*
(window, and attach full txs/witnesses for display.) Tj
T*
(- Fast tx lookup: get_tx_location\(txid\) and get_tx_by_id\(txid\) use blk:t:* first; legacy) Tj
T*
(backward scan is retained as a compatibility fallback.) Tj
T*
(- Startup backfill: when TX_INDEX_AUTO_BACKFILL=true \(default\), BlockStore backfills missing) Tj
T*
(blk:t:* entries once and marks meta:blk:txindex_ready=1.) Tj
T*
(- Tip tracking: latest_height scans blk:h: keys and validates stored index matches height.) Tj
T*
(- Resizing: put_block retries writes and uses the shared rollover helper. lmdb_status\(\) reports) Tj
T*
(remaining headroom.) Tj
T*
(- Integrity log: _append_chain_hash writes cumulative SHA3-384 header chain to) Tj
T*
(logs/<network>/state_hashes.log.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(UTXOStore \(Src/Storage/utxostorage.py\)) Tj
T*
(- Environment: Constants.DATABASES["utxo"].) Tj
T*
(- Keys:) Tj
T*
(- Primary: utxo:<txid-bytes>:<vout> \(record JSON\).) Tj
T*
(- Secondary address index: utxoaddr:<canonical_hpk>:<txid>:<vout> \(points to primary key\).) Tj
T*
(- Index-ready marker: meta:utxoaddr:index_ready.) Tj
T*
(- Operations: list by address, get/spend/apply_block. Write-heavy paths run through a bounded) Tj
T*
(retry wrapper so MapFullError triggers rollover growth up to the configured UTXO ceiling.) Tj
T*
(- Address lookup now uses a prefix scan on utxoaddr:* when index is ready) Tj
T*
(\(O\(utxos_for_address\)\), with legacy full-scan fallback while index is not ready.) Tj
T*
(- Index maintenance is done in the same LMDB write transaction on) Tj
T*
(put/spend/unspend/delete/apply/revert paths.) Tj
T*
(- Backfill: UTXOStore.backfill_address_index\(\) can rebuild secondary keys for existing datasets) Tj
T*
(and then mark meta:utxoaddr:index_ready=1.) Tj
T*
(- Optional safety compare: UTXO_ADDR_INDEX_SHADOW_COMPARE runs indexed + legacy lookup and logs) Tj
T*
(mismatch. UTXO_ADDR_INDEX_RETURN_LEGACY can force returning legacy results on mismatch.) Tj
T*
(- Consensus guard: uses utxostorage.consensus_write_context \(mirrors BlockStore pattern\) when) Tj
T*
(called from consensus.) Tj
T*
(- Amounts stored as Decimal-friendly strings; locking/spent flags persisted. Addresses are) Tj
T*
(canonicalized to HPK at write boundaries.) Tj
T*
(- Diagnostics: lmdb_status\(\) exposes current map utilization and next growth step.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(MempoolStore \(Src/Storage/mempool.py\)) Tj
T*
(- Environment: Constants.DATABASES["mempool"].) Tj
T*
(- Keys:) Tj
T*
(- tx:<txid> for raw tx JSON) Tj
T*
(- mempool:confirmed:<txid> tombstones) Tj
T*
(- mempool:meta:revision cross-process refresh marker) Tj
T*
(- in-memory UTXO reservation index map) Tj
T*
(- Features: add/remove tx, list pending, rebuild UTXO index from LMDB on startup, tombstone) Tj
T*
(confirmed txs.) Tj
T*
(- Runtime performance path: hot API reads use RAM snapshots/counters \(transactions, _ram,) Tj
T*
(_total_size_bytes, _total_fees\) instead of full LMDB scans.) Tj
T*
(- Cross-process coherence path: readers call _maybe_refresh_from_lmdb\(\) and skip full rebuilds) Tj
T*
(when mempool:meta:revision is unchanged.) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
